release.name: v0.2
release.body:
**Features:**
* Converting .ftex files to .dds
* Converting .dds to .ftex
* Converting all .ftex files in a directory to .dds
* :new: Unpacking .pftxs files to .ftex and .ftexs 
* :new: Repacking .ftex and .ftexs files to .pftxs 

**Issues:**
* ~~Cached mip maps get loaded when found in a .pftxs file~~
* When converting a dds file to ftex its type (Diffuse,Normal,Material,Cube) is not saved.
* When converting a dds file to ftex the amount of ftexs files can differ from the original amount

Filename | Issue
------------------ | -----------------------
fx_expanm06_ks_alp_clp.ftex  | Missing .6.ftexs file
gntn_common_ter_bsm.ftex     | Missing .6.ftexs file
gntn_common_ter_nrm.ftex     | Missing .6.ftexs file
gntn_common_ter_srm.ftex     | Missing .6.ftexs file
gntn_photo_clp.ftex          | Missing .6.ftexs file
afgh_irpl001_srm.ftex        | Invalid ftex file
